pipeline-mod-celia v1.2.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Celia-specific DTBook to PEF script with:
  - a Celia-specific default CSS style sheet with support for
    - simple tables
    - notes
    - `notransform` class for UTF-8 braille content that
      is to be passed through the system unchanged
    - ...
  - automatic insertion of title pages
  - XSLT pre-processing for tables containing forward slashes
  - enabled options `page-width`, `page-height`, `duplex`,
    `include-image-groups`, `include-images`, `include-captions`,
    `include-note-references`, `include-production-notes`,
    `show-braille-page-numbers`, `show-print-page-numbers`,
    `line-spacing`, `hyphenation` and `toc-depth`
  - an additional option `insert-titlepage`
  - an additional option `letter-spacing` (aggregates letter- and word-spacing in UI)
  (https://github.com/snaekobbi/pipeline-mod-celia/pull/7)
- Translation table changes
  - default behavior for undefined characters: replace with an asterisk
  - copyright and trademark symbols

pipeline-mod-celia v1.1.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Support for letter- and word-spacing

pipeline-mod-celia v1.0.0
=========================

Includes
--------
- Improved hyphenation table for Finnish (https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/2)
- Custom Liblouis based translator that handles `html:strong` and `html:em`
  (https://github.com/snaekobbi/liblouis/issues/1, https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/13,
  https://github.com/snaekobbi/issues/issues/14, https://github.com/snaekobbi/pipeline-mod-braille/issues/38)
